  "remarks": "\nMajor-general of the Russian Army. He was the commander of the 76th airborne division which was involved in the Russian military presence on the territory of Ukraine, notably during the illegal annexation of Crimea. Now Deputy Chief of Staff of the Airborne Forces.  \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
